cdata.name: IndiCoin
cdata.desc:
Indicoinis a social platform that aims to provide a tool where people can help thelessprivileged from any part of the world. This platform will leverage the Ethereum blockchain to provide meaningful tasks to the user community and attach a monetary value to it, creating a community of people who are incentivized to do socially positive and constructive tasks.

Indicointokens will give the users voting rights to decide either to accept or reject a suggested taskand also will able users to receive rewards for participating in tasks.
